text: Frank Parlow (born 22 April 1967) is a German former yacht racer who competed in the 1992 Summer Olympics and in the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:German male sailors (sport) Category:Olympic sailors of Germany Category:Sailors at the 1992 Summer Olympics – Tornado Category:Sailors at the 1996 Summer Olympics – Tornado Category:Tornado class world champions Category:World champions in sailing for Germany
title: Frank Parlow
